results.story: The Naruto Shippuden x ASICS Gel Lyte 3 OG Kakashi is drawn from a three-piece footwear collection celebrating the long-running anime series. Inspired by Kakashis Jounin outfit, the upper pairs navy suede overlays with a grey textile base, featuring a tearaway outer layer that reveals a lightning pattern that nods to Kakashis Chidori technique. The Mangekyou Sharingan symbol is displayed on the split tongue, while the Uzumaki clans red spiral is embroidered on the lateral forefoot. The sneaker rides on a grey EVA midsole with Gel cushioning in the heel.

results.story: The ASICS Gel Lyte 3 Academic Scholar Pack dresses the retro runner in a varsity-inspired color palette. Soft suede covers the majority of the upper in contrasting dark green and violet hues. Matching purple side stripes are outlined in yellow, with the vibrant hue reappearing on the plush textile that lines the collar and signature split tongue. The sneaker is mounted on a two-tone EVA midsole with Gel cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, a solid purple rubber outsole provides durable traction.
